The paper deals with the problem of robust distributed control, which is a topic that falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses optimization problems and the decomposition of information constraints, which are topics that fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.MA) and optimization and control (cs.LG). The paper also applies the developed techniques to the platooning of autonomous vehicles, which is a topic that falls under the categories of robotics (cs.RO) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
